Flatulence:

• Flatulence is better known as passing wind or passing gas
• Excessive gas in stomach and intestine is released in form of:
   o Flatulence
   o Burping
• It can become an embarrassing problem if one passes gas frequently

Symptoms to look for:

• Fullness in stomach
• Abdominal pain
• Belching

Causes:

• Rapid chewing or drinking leads to swallowing of excess air
• Carbonated drinks
• Lactase deficiency in the body

